summary: An ordinance relating to the improvement of The Alley in Blocks 3 and 4, Replat of Blocks 3, 4, 5, 6 and 13 in Replat of Green Lake Home Addition, et al., by paving, etc., Local Improvement District No. 5795, providing for an increase in the rate of interest payable on the bonds and assessments of said district, and amending Section 4 of Ordinance No. 76397.
